Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.33,0:00:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真 雷 你們在幹什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.71,0:00:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幹什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.33,0:00:08.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在模擬和Freedom的戰鬥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.63,0:00:10.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底有什麼事?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.30,0:00:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要做這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.42,0:00:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為他很強
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.72,0:00:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我希望大家現在能夠瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.85,0:00:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至今為止戰火卻不斷蔓延的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.10,0:00:26.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說到底 這場戰爭發生的真正原因
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.77,0:00:27.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.26,0:00:31.98,Default3,,0000,0000,0000,,PLANT最高評議會
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.36,0:00:28.98,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,諾伊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.23,0:00:30.73,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 克莉斯塔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.11,0:00:32.69,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,那是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.11,0:00:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,議長在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.53,0:00:37.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 關於這次播放我也完全…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.95,0:00:40.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 絕不能這樣下去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.83,0:00:42.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種整日互相傷害的世界中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.91,0:00:44.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會有安寧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.21,0:00:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那種無盡持續下去的仇恨連鎖反應
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.50,0:00:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們難道體驗得還不夠嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.09,0:00:56.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但卻有人無論如何都要阻礙這一切實現
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.59,0:00:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且是從很久以前開始
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.05,0:01:00.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,背後的他們
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.68,0:01:04.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總是熱衷於製造敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.23,0:01:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,熱衷於為世界帶來戰爭的軍事產業復合體
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.11,0:01:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死之商人 Logos
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.86,0:01:16.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們才是我們這些期盼和平的人們真正的敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.44,0:01:21.66,Default3,,0000,0000,0000,,奧布 內閣府官邸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.74,0:01:19.66,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,父親
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.08,0:01:21.45,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,哦 尤拉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.37,0:01:23.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.00,0:01:27.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,利塔 格魯皮亞 克勞德氏他們的名字居然都出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.21,0:01:35.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我從心底盼望著不再發生戰爭的和平世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.05,0:01:38.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因此 告訴那些欲加以阻撓的人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.22,0:01:42.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對於世界真正的敵人Logos
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.43,0:01:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在此宣佈一日不滅其根本誓不罷休
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.44,0:01:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,狄蘭達爾
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.44,0:01:55.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,展示出的人中有和賽蘭…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.20,0:01:59.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 是和奧布有著複雜關係的人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.53,0:02:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 不止是奧布
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.20,0:02:06.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根本就沒有任何國家和他們的全球化企業完全無關
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.29,0:02:10.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,狄蘭達爾議長到底有什麼打算
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.09,0:02:15.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 讓大家困擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.59,0:02:20.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我的想法正如剛才播放的內容
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.51,0:02:24.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開戰時防衛戰之際所說的話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.52,0:02:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,容我在這裏重複一次
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.64,0:02:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,手中再次拿起的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.64,0:02:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次必須成為終結一切戰鬥之物
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.73,0:02:36.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很擔心奧布
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.74,0:02:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今後賽蘭打算怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.36,0:02:44.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們也該從他們的戰爭系統中脫離出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.62,0:02:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們真正的敵人 不是聯合也不是自然人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.04,0:02:52.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不打倒Logos 只會一再重蹈覆轍
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.29,0:02:55.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 這談何容易
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.80,0:02:56.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.55,0:03:01.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在既然看不到通往和平的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.39,0:03:04.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們可選擇的道路也就僅此而已了不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.35,0:03:10.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,否則 這場戰爭永遠不會結束
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.73,0:03:12.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回去吧 瑪琉艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.65,0:03:14.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回奧布
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.77,0:03:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.57,0:03:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有些不同於以往的東西正在蠢蠢欲動
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.45,0:03:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有這種感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.37,0:03:27.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我贊成議長的意見
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.54,0:03:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正如他所說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.70,0:03:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次必須給這戰爭的歷史劃上休止符
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.29,0:03:33.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,確實
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.33,0:03:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.00,0:03:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也贊成
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.09,0:03:36.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,贊成
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.25,0:03:38.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,贊成
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.59,0:03:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向您的決斷與勇氣致敬
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.60,0:03:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.61,0:03:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-wax 006來電
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.02,0:03:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,區域3 地點1.36有不明物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.15,0:04:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為Archangel
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.28,0:04:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然有行動了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.49,0:04:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,報告司令部
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.41,0:04:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,另外重寫資料庫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.33,0:04:11.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那已經不是不明 而是敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.87,0:04:12.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.17,0:04:14.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艦隊司令部來電
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.33,0:04:20.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Minerva前往支援即將進行的Angel Down作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.15,0:06:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左舵10 繞進地面的陰影處
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.20,0:06:09.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Valient 發射
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.50,0:06:19.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瑪琉艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.44,0:06:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.07,0:06:45.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.07,0:06:49.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好 被他們壓制住了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.45,0:06:50.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.61,0:06:53.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是ZAFT為何突然這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.53,0:06:56.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來完全被包圍了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.33,0:06:58.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,右舷後方又出現BuCUE 8
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.50,0:07:01.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,10點方向也再出現BABI 9
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.25,0:07:02.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,導彈來襲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.63,0:07:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迴避
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.88,0:07:04.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.88,0:07:08.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.84,0:07:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我理解盡量避免無意義的戰鬥是這艘船的理念
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.72,0:07:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但這樣下去會被擊沉的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.97,0:07:16.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請下達直擊的許可
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.02,0:07:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果您不承認 至少讓我們的Murasame隊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.52,0:07:25.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白 但是基拉也說過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.73,0:07:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或許讓我們攻擊正是對方的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.49,0:07:30.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.32,0:07:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿瑪基上尉 讓我們出擊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.95,0:07:34.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Murasame一台也不能少
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.83,0:07:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全數帶回奧布
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.13,0:07:49.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要想辦法出海
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.67,0:07:51.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在此之前大家要堅持住
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.09,0:07:54.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目標 再向西10
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.60,0:07:58.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊魯隊BABI 全隊中彈 返航
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.43,0:08:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是傳說中的Freedom和Archangel
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.69,0:08:05.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫M.S.隊別太急躁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.86,0:08:08.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,否則支持不到Minerva趕來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.53,0:08:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正因為溫吞地驅趕才使我方漸漸不利
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.03,0:08:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算沒等到Minerva 只要出動全軍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.28,0:08:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道吧 阿拉斯加和雅金·多維戰役
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.83,0:08:26.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欲速則不達
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.84,0:08:32.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為長遠著想 還是讓Minerva和Impulse來了斷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.26,0:08:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,按命令交給我軍的王牌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.10,0:08:40.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,議長是說要打倒Logos
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.77,0:08:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那為何要去攻擊Archangel
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.94,0:08:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這道命令絕對有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.10,0:08:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請再一次向司令部…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.69,0:08:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經確認過了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.15,0:08:53.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是答覆不變
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.03,0:08:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不表明目的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.20,0:09:00.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一味擾亂戰場擴大戰火的Archangel和Freedom
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.58,0:09:06.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,考慮到今後局勢 必須剷除這個潛在的威脅
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.50,0:09:09.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是本國的決定
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.50,0:09:10.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.38,0:09:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經無能為力了 作戰早已開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.69,0:09:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,捕捉到A-wax傳來的信號
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.73,0:09:29.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,顯示情況圖
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.41,0:09:46.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也別再止足不前了 阿斯蘭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.88,0:09:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白你不想跟以前的戰友作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.30,0:09:55.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 時過境遷 人心也會改變的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.55,0:09:59.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不是也變了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.77,0:10:11.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好看著現在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.28,0:10:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艦長 已收到A-wax的信號
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.82,0:10:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即將到達作戰區域
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.28,0:10:20.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.70,0:10:26.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.96,0:10:32.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不想看的話就待在房間裏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.59,0:10:38.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過 和那艘船作戰我們也會以死相拼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.76,0:10:44.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艦橋遮蔽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.39,0:10:46.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發令紅色狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.48,0:10:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對艦對M.S.戰鬥準備
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.48,0:10:51.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發令紅色狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.02,0:10:54.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,駕駛員請在搭乘機內待命
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.19,0:10:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,CIWS Tristan Isolde啟動
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.99,0:11:01.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發射管一號至三號 全炮門裝填Parsifal
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.29,0:11:05.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.16,0:11:11.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的 你做得到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.64,0:11:23.60,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank You
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.39,0:11:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.82,0:11:38.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯蘭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.45,0:11:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,距離地點20 即將遇敵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.45,0:11:50.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發射干擾彈 Impulse出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.33,0:11:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.46,0:11:56.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,探測器…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.50,0:11:59.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是干擾彈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.38,0:12:01.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左舵10 下降
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.68,0:12:10.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真·飛鳥 核心戰機出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.55,0:12:43.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開始攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.57,0:13:07.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Minerva
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.12,0:13:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,捕捉到Archangel 距離2000
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.79,0:13:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isolde 發射
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.72,0:13:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.85,0:13:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.73,0:13:37.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會 為什麼那艘船要…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.56,0:13:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連那都能避開
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.40,0:13:42.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主角登場了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.15,0:13:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就讓庫拉提斯露兩手給我們看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.96,0:14:01.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊 別胡亂移動就不會中彈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.50,0:14:04.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然沒打算擊中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.22,0:14:09.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅琳 打開國際救援頻道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.89,0:14:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.77,0:14:15.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裏是ZAFT艦Minerva艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.85,0:14:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塔利雅·庫拉提斯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.94,0:14:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Archangel 聽得見嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.86,0:14:24.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艦長 Minerva發來的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.99,0:14:32.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本艦奉司令部命令前來擊沉貴艦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.00,0:14:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但如果貴艦現在停止包括艦載機在內的一切攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.34,0:14:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,投降的話 本艦也會停止攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.34,0:14:46.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.47,0:14:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,命令可是擊毀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.43,0:14:51.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,庫拉提斯這傢伙到底想幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.68,0:14:52.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.89,0:14:54.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,僅此一次警告
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.06,0:14:57.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,過時不候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.98,0:15:00.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向你們保證乘員的生命安全
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.69,0:15:05.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,望貴艦三思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.86,0:15:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.99,0:15:14.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是那艘Minerva的艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.04,0:15:16.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不想與之為敵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.16,0:15:19.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 如果在這裏向ZAFT投降
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.00,0:15:21.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡嘉莉大人的安全…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.42,0:15:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿瑪基
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.29,0:15:25.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.76,0:15:30.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去海上 送卡嘉莉回奧布
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.05,0:15:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以此為最優先
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.43,0:15:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基拉 怎麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.60,0:15:37.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,米莉雅麗亞 打開和對方相同的頻道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.81,0:15:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.02,0:15:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裏是Archangel艦長 瑪琉·拉米亞斯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.02,0:15:47.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感謝貴艦的好意 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.73,0:15:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.16,0:15:53.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.49,0:15:55.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 非常遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.62,0:15:57.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們無法接受
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.83,0:16:01.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本艦還有工作
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.67,0:16:03.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聯合還是PLANT
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.67,0:16:06.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,世界正被分為兩種顏色時
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.63,0:16:09.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本艦似乎又成了礙眼的顏色
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.13,0:16:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但正因為如此 更不能在這裏被抹去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.76,0:16:19.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,願能允許我們脫離
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.39,0:16:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,庫拉提斯這蠢貨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.23,0:16:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看看你幹了什麼蠢事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.02,0:16:29.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓M.S.隊重新開始攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.90,0:16:32.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被小看了 絕不允許他們逃離
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.42,0:16:44.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別逃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.25,0:16:46.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.09,0:16:49.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,維拉德隊長 怎麼自作主張
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.13,0:16:51.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不攻擊就會讓他們逃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.09,0:16:53.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們自己不也這麼說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.43,0:17:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算是FAITH
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.52,0:17:01.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如此膽小的婦人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.48,0:17:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被人羞辱怎能就此罷休
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.98,0:17:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Minerva不幹的話由我們來干
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.78,0:17:11.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.32,0:17:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 Archangel
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.21,0:17:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總是這一招
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.54,0:17:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別以為一直能奏效
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.80,0:17:38.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真 別…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.05,0:17:39.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基拉他…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.53,0:17:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Freedom的確動作迅速
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.49,0:17:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,射擊也準確
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.20,0:18:01.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但那台機體絕對不瞄準駕駛艙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.29,0:18:07.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,攻擊的總是武裝和主監視器
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.08,0:18:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impulse的勝機就在這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.48,0:18:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅琳 胸部組件 Force Silhouette
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.63,0:18:58.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.35,0:19:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說了別想逃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.98,0:19:14.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你殺了史黛拉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.74,0:19:22.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我都那麼拚命想阻止了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.12,0:19:30.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,距離海岸線10
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.17,0:19:32.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣支撐不下去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.63,0:19:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請出動Murasame
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.75,0:19:34.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甩掉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.17,0:19:36.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基拉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.67,0:19:38.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.01,0:19:41.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼這裏總是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.05,0:19:43.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.01,0:19:51.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你今天得在這裏被我打下來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.52,0:19:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼…到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.90,0:19:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅琳 Sword Silhouette
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.07,0:20:00.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.16,0:20:04.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即將到達海岸線
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.16,0:20:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會被逃脫的 艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.95,0:20:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tannhauser 啟動
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.54,0:20:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目標 Archangel
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.34,0:20:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,緊急隔離壁封閉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.05,0:20:19.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,準備下潛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.55,0:20:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.38,0:20:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基拉 基拉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.38,0:20:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基拉大人的話不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.39,0:20:26.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放出Rouge
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.39,0:20:27.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.56,0:20:28.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.37,0:20:56.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,趕快 讓它下潛就完了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.21,0:20:59.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發射
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.25,0:21:36.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.06,0:21:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成功了 史黛拉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.81,0:21:55.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣總算…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.82,0:22:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基拉!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.45,0:23:26.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,曾相信的是什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.49,0:23:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是他的話語
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.04,0:23:29.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是認為不會發生
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.75,0:23:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像萬花筒般變換意義的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.13,0:23:35.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是世界 還是自己的心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.34,0:23:40.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為戰士們準備的下一個舞台是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.43,0:23:44.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下集 機動戰士Gundam Seed Destiny
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.10,0:23:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,混沌的前方
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.18,0:23:50.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,降落到夢想的世界吧 Destiny
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.63,0:00:31.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-------------OPJP-------------
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.70,0:04:25.92,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,僕たちは迷いながら
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.92,0:04:30.95,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,たどり着く場所を探しつづけ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.95,0:04:35.34,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,悲しくて涙流しても
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.34,0:04:40.26,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,いつか輝きにかえて
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.36,0:04:51.70,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,閉ざした過去が今
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.70,0:04:53.98,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,胸を搖さぶるから
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.98,0:04:56.37,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,求めるほど遠く
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.37,0:04:58.80,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,置き去りの心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.80,0:05:03.44,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,僕らは生きるほど何かを失って
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.44,0:05:05.94,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,それでも明日への
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.94,0:05:08.15,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,夢を捨てたくない
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.15,0:05:12.84,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,悲しみの理由でさえも
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.84,0:05:17.34,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,つよく抱きしめていたい
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.34,0:05:22.78,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,通りすぎた季節のその先に
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.78,0:05:27.31,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,なにがあるのだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.73,0:05:34.06,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,僕たちは迷いながら
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.06,0:05:39.04,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,たどり着く場所を探しつづけ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.04,0:05:43.47,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,悲しくて涙流しても
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.47,0:05:48.38,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,いつか輝きにかえて
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.38,0:05:51.20,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,Cause I'm never gonna stop streak in my dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.93,0:02:50.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-------------OPCN-------------
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.70,0:04:25.92,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,我們充滿迷茫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.92,0:04:30.95,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,尋找安身之處
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.95,0:04:35.34,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,即使悲傷流淚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.34,0:04:40.26,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,最終將化作光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.36,0:04:51.70,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,過去封存的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.70,0:04:53.98,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,此刻撥動心弦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.98,0:04:56.37,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,追尋遙遠的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.37,0:04:58.80,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,被捨棄的心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.80,0:05:03.44,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,隨著時間我們漸漸失去了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.44,0:05:05.94,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,但對於明天
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.94,0:05:08.15,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,不願捨棄夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.15,0:05:12.84,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,即使有悲傷的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.84,0:05:17.34,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,也要緊緊擁抱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.34,0:05:22.78,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,逝去的季節的前方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.78,0:05:27.31,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,會是什麼顏色
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.73,0:05:34.06,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,我們充滿迷茫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.06,0:05:39.04,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,尋找安身之處
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.04,0:05:43.47,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,即使悲傷流淚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.47,0:05:48.38,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,最終將化作光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.38,0:05:51.20,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我從未停止追求夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.17,0:03:59.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-------------EDJP-------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.65,0:22:13.67,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,今でも氣付かないでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.67,0:22:18.78,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,この靜かな空に
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.73,0:22:28.75,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,いつでも思い出すけど
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.75,0:22:33.59,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,もうどこにももどれない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.35,0:22:42.38,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,そしてずっと心で醒めて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.38,0:22:46.59,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,そっと氣付いて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.59,0:22:51.66,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,いつかきっとやさしさ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.66,0:22:57.53,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,見えてくるように
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.53,0:23:01.86,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,What's stopping me? I get stuck again
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.86,0:23:07.61,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it really OK? It's never OK for me
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.61,0:23:11.86,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,What's got into me? I get lost again
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.86,0:23:18.90,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it really OK? It's never going to be
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.64,0:01:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-------------EDCN-------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.65,0:22:13.67,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,至今仍未察覺
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.67,0:22:18.78,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,在這寂靜的天空下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.73,0:22:28.75,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然仍然常常想起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.75,0:22:33.59,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,時光一去不復返
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.35,0:22:42.38,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,一直深藏於心中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.38,0:22:46.59,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,輕輕的告訴
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.59,0:22:51.66,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,這份溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.66,0:22:57.53,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,將映入眼簾
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.53,0:23:01.86,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼阻止了我嗎? 我再次停住
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.86,0:23:07.61,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,難道真的可以? 我從未確定
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.61,0:23:11.86,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼鑽進我的心中? 我再次得而復失
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.86,0:23:18.90,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,難道真的可以? 它永遠不會消失

